                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18261026-175-off972 t18261026-175-cd973"></join>, 4 shillings, and 9 half-pence
            </rs>, the monies of 
               <persName id="t18261026-175-victim1061" type="victimName">
                  John 
                  Brooksbank
               <interp inst="t18261026-175-victim1061" type="surname" value="Brooksbank"></interp>
